name: earth was nice while it lasted

content: Someone fired a round in to the window of The Taproom in Renton WA today around noon.  No one was inside so no one was harmed.  This is where RWers on fb have threatened to protest a Drag Story Hour.  Sign was put up by employees.

photo.alt: A window with a bullet hole with clear tape over the cracks.  A sign reads “what intolerance looks like” with a green arrow pointing at the hole is tapes just below the hole.  You can see the reflection of vehicles in the window.
